Subject: The server returned a "500 Internal Server Error".
Description: The server returned a "500 Internal Server Error".
What_We_Know__c: The disk space of the EPP Server got filled up with e-mail alerts which were not being sent because their email server settings were modified.
Next_Steps__c: A remote session was set in order to help them to configure the e-mail server settings.
Solution_Comment__c: Disk space was cleared from backend.
